👉 “In traditional setup (Maven → Tomcat), we use two servers. In Docker, both stages are inside one Dockerfile. So are stages just logical separation, not physical servers?”

👉 “Does each FROM create a completely new isolated filesystem like a fresh server?”

👉 “If stages are independent, how exactly does COPY --from=build work internally?”

⚙️ 2. Image Size & Optimization (VERY IMPORTANT)

