👉 “Is multi-stage build mainly for reducing image size or also for security?”

👉 “What happens if I don’t use multi-stage and deploy directly with Node?”

👉 “When should I use node:alpine vs node:18?”

🚀 3. Runtime vs Build-Time

👉 “Why do we need Node.js only in Stage 1 and not in Stage 2?”

👉 “What exactly is inside /app/build? Is it pure HTML/CSS/JS?”

👉 “Can React app run without Node in production?”

